# 🧠 Approach 1: Count Each Direction

### 🔹 Java

```java
class Solution {
    public boolean judgeCircle(String moves) {
        int countU = 0, countD = 0, countL = 0, countR = 0;

        for(char c : moves.toCharArray()){
            if(c == 'U') countU++;
            else if(c == 'D') countD++;
            else if(c == 'L') countL++;
            else countR++;
        }

        return countU == countD && countL == countR;
    }
}
```

### 🔹 Python3

